1986. A man's dream are coming true, as he buy his new vehicle using his first salary. The proud wife takes his selfie with the new vehicle. Behind him are the vast wide ocean and blue skies. The possibilities seems endless, his dreams are immense, and life seems perfect enough.

My love for "pop art" colors makes me use this color as my illustration style in the future. The process of for this NFT took 3 weeks, which is a long time for me as I have not much time left to work on my passion projects.
